+<!DOCTYPE html>
+<html>
+<head><title>Chameleon Pierce Test</title></head>
+<body>
+<h1>Shadow DOM Pierce Test (Turnstile-like structure)</h1>
+
+<h2>Test 1: Simple Closed Shadow DOM</h2>
+<div id="host1"></div>
+<p id="result1">Waiting...</p>
+
+<h2>Test 2: Nested Closed Shadow DOM (2 levels)</h2>
+<div id="host2"></div>
+<p id="result2">Waiting...</p>
+
+<h2>Test 3: Turnstile-like (closed shadow > iframe > closed shadow > checkbox)</h2>
+<div id="host3"></div>
+<p id="result3">Waiting...</p>
+
+<h2>Test 4: Deep pierce - click checkbox from outside all layers</h2>
